OL,5, Ministers plan to force all ferry      
OL,6, companies operating from UK ports to   
OL,7, pay at least the National Minimum Wage,
OL,8, in a bid to persuade P&O Ferries to    
OL,9, reinstate 800 workers it has sacked.   
OL,11,FA source says Transport Secretary Grant
OL,12,FShapps hopes the firm will "see reason 
OL,13,Fand step back".                        
OL,15,FBut unions have said workers should be 
OL,16,Freinstated on their existing terms not 
OL,17,Fthe National Minimum Wage.             
OL,19,FIt comes as officials meet rivals to   
OL,20,Fprevent possible Easter travel issues. 
